description: Nina Bahinskaya had joined a women's march in Minsk as protests against the president continue.
title: Belarus protests: Opposition icon, 73, among hundreds detained in Minsk
title_page: Belarus protests: Opposition icon, 73, among hundreds detained in Minsk - BBC News
maintext: The opposition movement has been led by three women but only one, Maria Kolesnikova, has not gone into exile. She was charged with incitement to undermine national security days after allegedly ripping up her passport when the authorities tried to expel her from the country.
